      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-e" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>Recently, a savage herd of <FONT color=#a82424>werewolves</FONT> appeared in the <FONT color=#a82424>Blue Wind Plains</FONT> and has been scaring the residents and stealing their animals. Their alpaca fur, meat and carpet industry has suffered a great deal.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-f" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-f" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I hope you'll give me a reward too.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-f" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Justice prevails!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-f" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'll help you since I have no choice.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Fargeau$<BR>So <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, can you go and beat up those scary werewolves and rescue any residents who are held captive?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1823_merca_fargeau-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
